[Placeholder describing Experiment 2 design.
 Among MCCs that received the Lactoscan analyzer in Experiment 1, we randomly
 assign quality bonuses that create explicit price incentives for milk quality.
 This exogenously activates the price channel (sets alpha > 0 in the model).]
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Intervention
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "subsec:exp2-intervention"

\end_inset

[Placeholder describing the quality bonus intervention.
 Farmers delivering milk above a fat content threshold receive a price bonus.
 The bonus creates a direct link between measured quality and price, which
 was absent under the enforcement-only equilibrium observed in Experiment
 1.]
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Two Stages
