[Placeholder describing the two-stage design of Experiment 2.
 Stage 1 uses a lower fat threshold (3.3%) that most farmers can achieve.
 Stage 2 raises the threshold (3.9%) to test whether farmers respond to
 more demanding quality standards.
 This allows us to examine the intensive margin of quality improvement.]
